Subject: [PATCH] ui: Glance — hold modifier + click to open a peek overlay

Implements the Glance peek modal: hold a modifier key (default: Alt)
and click any link to open it in a floating overlay without navigating
away from the current page.

The overlay is a full WebContents rendered in a Views BubbleDialogDelegate
positioned over the tab content area. It is dismissed by:
  - Pressing Escape
  - Clicking outside the overlay
  - Navigation in the underlying tab

The overlay WebContents is isolated: no cookies from the parent tab are
shared; referrer is stripped.

CSS tokens: --fnc-glance-* (width, height, radius, shadow, blur, animations)

TODO: Stub. Full implementation in Phase 2.
      Tracked: fennec-browser/fennec#15
      Reference: Zen Browser Glance, Arc Browser Peek

PILLAR: Calm UI
JOURNAL: Requests made inside the Glance overlay are logged in the
